OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHouseholds face #3,000 hit 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom Budget measures, warns
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fthink tank                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Households will pay #3,000 more tax a  
OL,6, year as a result of measures introduced
OL,7, since Boris Johnson came to power,     
OL,8, including Wednesday's Budget, says the 
OL,9, Resolution Foundation.                 
OL,11,FThe think tank found policies announced
OL,12,Fby Chancellor Rishi Sunak had boosted  
OL,13,Fincomes by 2.8% for the poorest fifth  
OL,14,Fof households.                         
OL,16,FHowever, households on middle incomes  
OL,17,Fwould take a 2% hit, it added.         
OL,19,FIt also said the UK was in the worst   
OL,20,Fdecade for pay growth since the 1930s. 
